
依赖：

1.PHP5

>	sudo apt-get install php5

2.php-mem php-redis php-mysql php-mongo扩展

>	sudo apt-get install php5-memcache
>	sudo apt-get install php5-memcached
>	sudo apt-get install php5-redis
>	sudo apt-get install php5-mysql
>	sudo apt-get install php5-mongo

3.Php-fpm

>	sudo apt-get install php5-fpm

4.Nginx

>	sudo apt-get install nginx

5.Mysql

>	sudo apt-get install mysql
>	sudo apt-get install mysql-dev

6.Mongo

>	sudo apt-get install mongo

7.Memcache

>	sudo apt-get install memcache

8.Redis

>	sudo apt-get install redis-server

9.Yii

	下载[Yii](https://github.com/yiisoft/yii)框架源码，解压缩,当前工程目录下建立到YII框架的软链接

>	git clone https://github.com/yiisoft/yii.git

10.bootstrap

>	下载[bootstrap](http://v3.bootcss.com/)源码，在当前工程根目录下建立软连接


